===Etymology===
As the initial of the {{lang|zh|罙}} phonetic series is uncertain, {{zh-l|探}} may be related to {{zh-l|深}} (provided the initial was *''nh-'') ({{zh-ref|Schuessler, 2007}}).

Alternatively, this agrees with {{cog|lus|tham||to feel ''(especially with the hand)''}}.

Note also potential similarities to {{cog|my|စမ်း|t=to grope; to test}} ({{zh-ref|Luce, 1981}}).

